{
  "stem": "7832.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he-- that was-- you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I guess we lived off of that stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had a beautiful, beautiful vegetable garden, with tomatoes and string beans and all that stuff, in the backyard.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had a big backyard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course he grew spruce treats-- trees, and they were lined up along our property by the fence.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were little ones and big ones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They always looked so beautiful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And at Christmas time, I wanted to have a Christmas tree.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I wanted one of those trees to-- because all my non-Jewish friends had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were so busy, you know, with Christmas, and they were wrapping their own candies with special papers, and it just looked like a lot of fun.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was helping doing their candy, and I wanted some of my own, but my grandfather said, you're not allowed to have-- we don't celebrate Christmas, and we're not allowed to have one in the house.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I had an idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I-- we had a sukkah that was attached to the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And at-- at sukkahs, the roof opened up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when it wasn't sukkah, it was inside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I said to my grandfather, why don't we open up the roof and then put the Christmas tree in there, and then we'll have-- it will be outside.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It wouldn't be in the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he said, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's too cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It's too cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We can't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You can pick out any one you like, and that will be yours, but it's got to stay there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So I picked out one that grew in the garden.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the glitters from the snow, I made believe it was the decorations, and that was my Christmas tree.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did everything together.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
